contentrichtext.text: {{Infobox protected area of Australia | name = Byfield National Park | iucn_category = II | image = | caption = | locator_x = | locator_y = | nearest_town_or_city = | coordinates = {{Coord|22|47|02|S|150|43|54|E|type:landmark_region:AU-QLD|display=inline,title}} | area = {{Convert|87|km2|sqmi|1|abbr=on}} | established = 1988 | visitation_num = | visitation_year = | managing_authorities = [[Queensland Parks and Wildlife Service]] | official_site = }} '''Byfield''' is a national park in [[Queensland]], [[Australia]], 70 km north-east of [[Rockhampton]].<ref>[http://www.nprsr.qld.gov.au/parks/byfield/ Byfield National Park and Conservation Park]. Department of National Parks, Recreation, Sport and Racing. Retrieved 15 May 2013.</ref> The parks encloses 12 km of coastline including four beaches.<ref name="bofqc">{{cite book |title=Beaches of the Queensland Coast, Cooktown to Coolangatta: A Guide to Their Nature, Characteristics, Surf and Safety |last=Short |first=Andrew D. |year=2000 |publisher=Sydney University Press |isbn=0958650411 |page=236 |url=http://books.google.com.au/books?id=qEs92AQ5gfYC |accessdate=12 May 2013}}</ref> To the north of the national park is [[Shoalwater Bay]] and Byfield State Forest is located to the west of Byfield National Park. The park contains a number of [[four-wheel drive]] tracks and camping areas.<ref name="bmp">{{cite web |url=http://www.greatsoutheast.com.au/gsec2cqw/story.asp?weekID=1017&storyID=4706 |title=Byfield Miners Playgrounds |date=3 November 2012 |work=Queensland Weekender |accessdate=12 May 2013 }}</ref> Water Park Creek within the park contains a population of [[Rhadinocentrus ornatus]], a small freshwater fish species.<ref name="fwf">{{cite book |title=Freshwater Fishes of North-Eastern Australia |last=Pusey |first=Brad |coauthors=Mark Kennard, Angela Arthington |year=2004 |publisher=Csiro Publishing |isbn=064309895X |page=199 |url=http://books.google.com.au/books?id=yqmPm7iQEIMC |accessdate=12 May 2013}}</ref> ==See also== {{Portal|Queensland}} * [[Protected areas of Queensland]] {{-}} ==References== {{reflist}} {{National Parks of Queensland}} [[Category:National parks of Queensland]] [[Category:Protected areas established in 1988]] [[Category:Central Queensland]] {{Queensland-national-park-stub}}
